content: wtfsayo: Led a massive refactoring effort with 26 merged PRs, including significant CLI improvements in #5016 (+12.6k/-20.6k lines) and server package separation in #5122 (+14.9k/-13.5k lines), while enhancing the UI with improved styling in #5111 and #5105.
